The paper proposes a novel approach to utilize convolutional neural networks for time series forecasting, which is a common problem in machine learning. The paper focuses on comparing the proposed approach with conventional recurrent strategies on two datasets, which suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories.
